Throwback to my feature in @people magazine last year 💜 I still can’t believe this is my life 🙈 Some of you may not know that I’m an Army Veteran. I was lucky enough to serve my country. Besides being a Beauty Influencer, being a solider was my dream job. I was devastated when I was severely injured & was medically discharged from the military.
